""SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`InvoiceId`, `c`.`ClientId`, `c`.`CompanyId`, `c`.`IdentifierId`, `c`.`ProductId`, `c`.`Timestamp`, `c`.`Type`, `c`.`UserId`, `c.Company`.`Id`, `c.Company`.`Address`, `c.Company`.`City`, `c.Company`.`ClientId`, `c.Company`.`Code`, `c.Company`.`CompanyName`, `c.Company`.`IdentifierId`, `c.Company`.`ImageSrc`, `c.Company`.`InvoiceId`, `c.Company`.`Name`, `c.Company`.`TelephoneNumber`, `c.Company`.`Timestamp`, `c.Company`.`UserId`, `c.Client`.`Id`, `c.Client`.`AFM`, `c.Client`.`Address`, `c.Client`.`City`, `c.Client`.`Client_Occupation`, `c.Client`.`Code`, `c.Client`.`CompanyId`, `c.Client`.`CompanyName`, `c.Client`.`DOY`, `c.Client`.`Email`, `c.Client`.`IdentifierId`, `c.Client`.`TelephoneNumber`, `c.Client`.`Timestamp`, `c.Client`.`UserId`, `c.Client`.`ZipCode`, `c.Invoice`.`Id`, `c.Invoice`.`ClientId`, `c.Invoice`.`Code`, `c.Invoice`.`Comments`, `c.Invoice`.`CompanyId`, `c.Invoice`.`Description`, `c.Invoice`.`Discount`, `c.Invoice`.`IdentifierId`, `c.Invoice`.`Invoice_Type`, `c.Invoice`.`Number`, `c.Invoice`.`PriceAfterDiscount`, `c.Invoice`.`PriceBeforeDiscount`, `c.Invoice`.`PricePerUnit`, `c.Invoice`.`Quantity`, `c.Invoice`.`Timestamp`, `c.Invoice`.`Vat`
FROM `Pdfs` AS `c`
LEFT JOIN `Companies` AS `c.Company` ON `c`.`CompanyId` = `c.Company`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN `Clients` AS `c.Client` ON `c`.`ClientId` = `c.Client`.`Id`
